      <title>三星工人计划“无限期”罢工，全球科技业面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/samsung-labor-union-says-prepared-to-strike-indefinitely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司超过 28,000 名员工的工会宣布无限期罢工，此举威胁到这家全球最大存储芯片制造商的生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-10/samsung-labor-union-says-prepared-to-strike-indefinitely</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 00:58:46 GMT</pubDate>
