    <item>
      <title>苹果个人电脑季度出货量增长，涨幅最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/apple-acer-see-biggest-gains-as-quarterly-pc-shipments-jump-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司公布第二季度个人电脑出货量增长 21%，是全球个人电脑制造商中增幅最大的一次，这表明行业正在复苏，并连续第二个季度实现增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/apple-acer-see-biggest-gains-as-quarterly-pc-shipments-jump-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 21:24:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>休斯顿努力应对贝丽尔的停电和酷热</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/lumen-s-houston-data-center-having-disruptions-amid-power-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[休斯顿正在努力应对飓风贝丽尔造成的混乱后果，预计风暴洪水退去后，停电、道路阻塞、互联网中断和天然气供应不稳定等状况仍将持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-09/lumen-s-houston-data-center-having-disruptions-amid-power-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jul 2024 18:36:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
